{"tid":45404,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"麻友友性感聖誕裝扮惹網友熱議","createTime":"2016-12-19T02:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T05:24:51.000Z","uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ffc475b7b58b51bc717ec33fde1fd680648c451","tid":45404,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:56:31.000Z","msg":"據日本通網站報導，AKB48兼NGT48的柏木由紀公開了AKB48渡邊麻友的聖誕裝照片，引發熱議。柏木於2日在自己的推特上寫道：「麻友友聖誕老人」，並公布了身著聖誕服的渡邊的照片。<br />\n<br />\n對此，網友發起了熱評：「等待麻友友聖誕老人」「也期待有機磷（柏木由紀暱稱）聖誕老人。」等。另外，渡邊也在自己的推特上回應道：「麻友友的攝影師，有機磷。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2OL2sf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2OL2sf.jpg&h=14933cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978652aae0ac505b6840cdd20a8e191895e67901","tid":45404,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:57:26.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"3905a3ba10f596cc4936a0ca515ea35a0c37af09","tid":45404,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:58:10.000Z","msg":"哇，好靚既女孩子牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cecb50d4d34bcb7d9e91e6ee5c54a8670d15bb","tid":45404,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"